Medicaid Endpoint

Source: R/S7_caid.R
caid.Rd

Medicaid Endpoint

Medicaid Endpoint Group

Usage

caid_endpoint(alias)

caid_group(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> title alias

Value

An S7 <caid_endpoint> object.

An S7 <caid_group> object.

Examples

caid_endpoint("MLR")
#> <caid_endpoint>
#>  @ title     : chr "MLR Summary Reports"
#>  @ identifier: chr "https://data.medicaid.gov/api/1/datastore/query/743f9f04-4473-41e2-9da2-9a89db65ee55/0"
#>  @ metadata  : <caid_metadata>
#>  .. @ description: chr "The MLR Summary Reports provide plan-specific MLRs for Medicaid managed care programs. The MLR summary report d"| __truncated__
#>  .. @ modified   : Date[1:1], format: "2024-11-04"
#>  .. @ dictionary : chr NA
#>  .. @ download   : chr "https://download.medicaid.gov/data/mlr-public-use-file-07302024final.csv"
#>  @ dimensions: <caid_dimensions>
#>  .. @ limit : int 8000

#>  .. @ pages : int 1
#>  .. @ fields:List of 14
#>  .. .. $ state                                            : chr "state"

#>  .. .. $ mco_pihp_or_pahp_name                            : chr "mco_pihp_or_pahp_name"
#>  .. .. $ mlr_reporting_period_start_date                  : chr "mlr_reporting_period_start_date"
